{"tid":569101,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跟團遊中山 21人食物中毒","createTime":"2018-02-22T11:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-22T11:27:55.000Z","uid":84436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0e286fe24c36421fd939bc750e8418178e751d2d","tid":569101,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180222/57862511\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180222%2F57862511&d=jy%2FSht6CnzJSEoys9N7VJwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=f052b577\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180222%2F57862511&h=34a0f451\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180222/57862511</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n達美旅遊一個旅行團，周一（19日）在中山市南環路林場飯店享用午餐後懷疑食物中毒，衞生防護中心正調查個案。中心指，該團21名10至68歲團友，曾在涉事食肆進食包括蠔、魚、豬及家禽等中菜，飯後約8至59小時相繼出現腹瀉、腹痛及嘔吐等病微，其中11人曾到北區醫院急症室或私家診所求醫，毋須入院，全部人情況穩定。中心發言人指，會與達美旅遊保持聯繫，並已將個案通知廣東省衞生部門。<br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心建議，在外進食時避免吃生的海產，宜小心選擇冷盤，包括自助餐的刺身、壽司及生蠔，火鍋或燒烤時則要確保食物已徹底煮熟，及光顧可靠及持牌食肆。中心又提醒，鹽、醋、酒及日本芥茉均沒有殺菌效用。"},{"pid":"029996b1e279ac3e3ff27df29524d82b7a03c393","tid":569101,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T11:26:58.000Z","msg":"最衰都係佔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"723745c3b7d4b7e22323d4dbebd3f6a2644f0142","tid":569101,"uid":29090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-22T11:27:55.000Z","msg":"老豆老母成日去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}